"The beer is clear and golden with an inch of white head. The aroma is weak, offering grains, malt, sweetness. Crisp and clean. refreshing, though too grainy. Notes of corn and sweet alcohol. A beer for the masses, or to be consumed for free while gigging at a place such as this. I'm just glad guys like me can drink beers like this while playing music like that for people like them."
